data.description: Welcome to this 3 bedroom, 2 1/2 bathroom home with an office, partially finished basement, and 3-car garage.  This home offers a great combination of comfort, functionality, and potential for customization to fit your needs and preferences.  The main living area consists of a spacious open floor plan, combining the kitchen, dining, and living rooms, making it perfect for entertaining guests or spending quality time with family.  The kitchen is equipped with modern appliances, plenty of counter space, and storage options.  This home also features a Primary bedroom that includes an en-suite bathroom and 2 closets for convenience and privacy.  Additionally, it includes a home office space that is ideal for those who work remotely or need a designated area for studying. One of the highlights is the partially finished basement. This area offers endless possibilities, whether you want to transform it into a rec room, home gym, or a media center.  Lastly, this home includes a 3-car garage providing ample parking and storage space for your everyday needs.
